According to research by online parenting support site Mumsnet, women do twice as much housework as men even when they have done a full day in the office. There are 2 x 6-hour vouchers up for grabs, valued at R228 each. The lucky mom's will be able to book a home cleaning from their phone, tablet or computer and then sit back and relax while a trusted, insured SweepStar gives the place a great clean. 97% of SweepStars are moms and here some of them talk about their incredible & inspiring journeys and what being a mother makes them feel like. Here's to all empowering, inspiring, working mothers!   